      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "When the storms of life come, the wicked are whirled away,\n\tbut
        the godly have a lasting foundation.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Lazy people irritate their employers,\n\tlike vinegar to the teeth
        or smoke in the eyes.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Fear of the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> lengthens one\u2019s life,\n\tbut
        the years of the wicked are cut short.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The hopes of the godly result in happiness,\n\tbut the expectations
