  - verses:
    - title: 
      content: "To learn, you must love discipline;\n\tit is stupid to hate correction.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "The <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps> approves of those who are good,\n\tbut
        he condemns those who plan wickedness.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Wickedness never brings stability,\n\tbut the godly have deep roots.  "
      comments: []
